				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\text {CO}_2$$\end{document} storage pilot site in Germany (Bergmann et al. 2012; Schmidt-Hattenberger et al. 2016). TL-ERT is promising in this regard since abnormal resistivity increases can be interpreted as CO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
